title: Half of CS220 syllabus in two days. Possible?
body: I have my CS220 final exam on Saturday evening, and I know nothing about Pandas or webpages. does anyone have any good resources to use to learn these concepts?
comments: First how have you competed the assignments till now? Second, yes it’s possible. Very hard to fail a class with less than 7% of student getting less than a B. If you put some effort you can get AB
Do you know SQL? A decent amount of the Pandas stuff is just SQL queries.
